snippet.title: Missing Victorian woman found safe
snippet.content: A missing Victorian woman whose backpack was discovered on a Gold Coast beach has been found. Police confirmed on Monday afternoon that 40-year-old Gail Elizabeth Oliver has been located safe and well. It followed an earlier appeal for information after a member of the public found her backpack on Kurrawa Beach at Broadbeach about 6.15am. A search of the beach and water had failed to locate the 40-year-old, who was reported missing in her home state. Originally published as
